><strong style="color:#CC7832">ftp_get_option()</strong></span> 实例 </strong></p>      <div class="example-contents"> <div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"> <span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br /></span><span style="color: #FF8000">//&nbsp;Get&nbsp;the&nbsp;timeout&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;given&nbsp;FTP&nbsp;stream<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$timeout&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">ftp_get_option</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$conn_id</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">FTP_TIMEOUT_SEC</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span> </span> </span></div>      </div>      </div>     <p class="para">      参见 <span class="function">{@link ftp_set_option()}</span>。     </p>    </div>    <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.ftp.php">FTP 函数</a></div></div>
